2026-06-04T05:00:00.000Z | Scene: Crale docks, pre-dawn | A big sellsword (Aldric Thorne) cornered me and leaned hard — no subtlety, all threat. I nearly broke. But I've seen what the silver-eyed ones do, and I held. Gave him nothing. I am now afraid of TWO things, and one of them knows where I work. A hooded watcher saw the whole thing.
